channel.title: Carefully Reckless
channel.description: Are y’all ready to REALLY talk?! Well, join the conversation! Comedian and Actress Jessica “Jess Hilarious” Moore is now taking her “no hold bar” topics to The Black Effect Network introducing “Carefully Reckless”. She will be talking all the topics nobody DARES to speak about! From politics to entertainment, a one stop shop of all the buzzing topics to her infamous “Jess With The Mess” segments. Get ready to laugh, cry, or even shout out; whatever you do be prepared to be entertained!
